Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.73,0:00:05.32,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Dot in Champuru Town, \N and Roy in Fridge Town...{At Champuru Town Dot, at Fridge Town Roy}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.32,0:00:08.91,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Each of them passed their \N Terastal Course implementation tests.{have each passed their Terastal Course implementation tests.}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.74,0:00:13.08,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Next, it’s finally my turn!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.12,0:00:19.12,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Which is why we’re headed \N to the Mt. Nappé Gym, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.38,0:00:23.88,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,It’s too cold!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.71,0:00:28.59,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,I’m cold, I’m tired, I’m cold, I’m tired...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.64,0:00:38.02,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Even I’m starting to feel the chill...{Sasuga. line}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.02,0:00:40.77,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Liko, are you really sure \N there’s a Gym out here?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.44,0:00:43.94,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,We should be nearly there, I think...
Comment: 10,0:00:43.94,0:00:47.57,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Ahh... Ahh... Ahhhh...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.57,0:00:49.36,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,I can’t!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.36,0:00:51.32,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,I can’t walk another step.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.32,0:00:54.53,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,I’ll spend the last of my days \N lying here in the snow...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.99,0:00:57.25,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,The Gurumin Channel \N is finished, too...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.54,0:01:00.54,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Thanks for all your support, \N everyone...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.17,0:01:11.34,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Ahh... I’m seeing things... \N Death has come for me...
Comment: 10,0:01:11.18,0:01:12.18,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.18,0:01:14.30,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.30,0:01:15.72,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.10,0:01:24.65,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Comment: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:25.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Comment: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:55.70,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.79,0:03:09.25,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Got it. Thank you for having me!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.21,0:03:17.55,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,{\q2}They said I’d have to wait a while \N before they were ready to do my implementation test.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.55,0:03:20.10,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Then let’s go give {\i1}that{\i0} a try!{alt that uses a flubbish take for the Then: In the meantime, let’s give *that* a try!}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.22,0:03:23.18,Main,Human,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.52,0:03:31.11,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,Arukujira. Land Whale Pokémon. \N Ice type.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.48,0:03:35.99,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,It left the ocean and began living on land \N a very long time ago.{Partial Scarlet dex entry}{ENgame was fine, lifted directly}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.99,0:03:40.12,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,It lives in frigid areas, \N in pods of five or so individuals.{Partial Violet dex entry}{ENgame: It lives in frigid regions in pods of five or so individuals.}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.49,0:03:46.58,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Looks like Arukujira-sledding \N is booming in this area lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.58,0:03:48.92,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,People hop on \N the backs of trained Arukujira...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.92,0:03:51.71,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,...and ride them like sleds \N down the slopes!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.71,0:03:53.92,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,That sounds super fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.88,0:03:58.01,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,We’ve got some time to kill. \N Let’s give it a try!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.63,0:04:00.01,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.01,0:04:02.47,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,But my test will be coming up soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.64,0:04:08.44,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote? And even Terapagos...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.44,0:04:10.44,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,They all wanna try it, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.44,0:04:12.73,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,You never know, \N it could be a good warm-up!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.73,0:04:15.65,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,You’re right. \N Okay, maybe just for a bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.65,0:04:17.11,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,What do you say, Nyarote?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.49,0:04:20.91,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.29,0:04:28.50,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,We’re gonna crash!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.00,0:04:35.59,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Whoa! That’s my Hogator!{Sasuga. line}
Comment: 10,0:04:39.51,0:04:41.76,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.60,0:04:47.68,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Thanks, Welcamo.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.68,0:04:49.56,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.06,0:04:54.61,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Whoops...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.24,0:05:03.20,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.82,0:05:04.66,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.79,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Wow! It’s so pretty!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.34,0:05:20.01,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Ah! Terapagos!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.93,0:05:24.39,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.39,0:05:26.01,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,It’ll be safer for you{to stay} in the bag.{It’s dangerous, so stay in the bag.}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.94,0:05:34.19,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.19,0:05:38.07,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yukihami. Caterpillar Pokémon. \N Ice/Bug type.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.07,0:05:39.44,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,{\an8}It eats snow that has accum—{Scarlet Dex entry, interrupted.}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.86,0:05:38.99,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I wasn’t talking to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.44,0:05:39.94,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.24,0:05:48.41,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote, look up ahead!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.87,0:05:52.21,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I can’t stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.87,0:05:53.92,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,A cliff?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.31,0:06:10.22,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,That was a close one!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.22,0:06:12.14,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Thank you, Nyarote.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.44,0:06:15.98,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Liko!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.98,0:06:17.44,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.07,0:06:21.15,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Sorry... I almost fell off this cliff.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.15,0:06:22.40,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,A cliff?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.78,0:06:24.74,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,I mean, even if you {\i1}did{\i0} fall off here...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.74,0:06:25.49,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.70,0:06:28.70,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.58,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Either way, I’m glad you’re okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.62,0:06:33.87,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Yeah, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.87,0:06:36.75,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Geez, you’re such a scatterbrain.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.34,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Enjoying yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.01,0:06:51.22,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,If {\i1}that’s{\i0} enough to raise your spirits, \N you’re pretty frigid.{056}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.73,0:06:54.06,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Mr. Grusha{Honorifics note: Grusha-san}...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.06,0:06:55.98,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Wait... That’s Liko’s...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.98,0:06:59.32,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Yeah. The Gym Leader \N of Mt. Nappé Gym.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.15,0:07:03.24,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,If you’re goofing off right before \N your implementation test,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.24,0:07:04.57,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,you must feel confident.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.95,0:07:05.82,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.24,0:07:09.24,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,You had better be prepared \N to heat me up.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.62,0:07:12.37,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,Arukujira. Let’s go.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.05,0:07:26.01,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,We’re back! \N That was so much fun, mister!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.34,0:07:29.72,Main,Human,0,0,0,,Come back for more anytime!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.43,0:07:35.39,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Mr. Grusha{Honorifics note: Grusha-san} was just as harsh \N as the rumors made him out to be...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.39,0:07:36.94,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.94,0:07:37.94,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.69,0:07:44.86,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Isn’t that Mr. Grusha{Honorifics note: Grusha-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.86,0:07:45.82,Main,Human,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.82,0:07:51.08,Main,Human,0,0,0,,That’s an article from after Grusha \N won a pro snowboarding tournament.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.70,0:07:54.75,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,So Mr. Grusha{Honorifics note: Grusha-san}’s a snowboarder!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.87,0:08:00.21,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,But... he seems so different \N compared to now.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.21,0:08:03.84,Main,Human,0,0,0,,Grusha’s our pride here on Mt. Nappé!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.13,0:08:11.68,Main,Human,0,0,165,,He was a talented snowboarder, \N winning many tournaments at a young age.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.51,0:08:15.98,Main,Human,0,0,165,,But then one year, \N during a tournament...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.36,0:08:32.95,Main,Human,0,0,165,,Grusha’s injuries led him to \N retire from snowboarding. {TL: Those injuries led Grusha to retire from snowboarding.}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.93,0:08:59.81,Main,Human,0,0,165,,But that wasn’t enough to break him.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.81,0:09:07.44,Main,Human,0,0,165,,The next path he chose was \N to become a Pokémon Trainer.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.03,0:09:12.95,Main,Human,0,0,165,,And now, he’s risen all the way up to serving as \N Gym Leader at the Mt. Nappé Gym.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.20,0:09:17.45,Main,Human,0,0,165,,He produced impressive results \N on an entirely different path.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.45,0:09:20.75,Main,Human,0,0,165,,{\t(2192,3192,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF)}He’s something else.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.75,0:09:22.83,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,No kidding...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.83,0:09:25.46,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Mr. Grusha{Honorifics note: Grusha-san}’s incredible.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.46,0:09:28.26,Main,Human,0,0,0,,Though... \N He {\i1}could{\i0} have kept snowboarding.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.84,0:09:30.22,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Then why didn’t he?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.22,0:09:34.01,Main,Human,0,0,0,,I figure he couldn’t get the kind of results \N he was hoping for anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.01,0:09:36.60,Main,Human,0,0,0,,He puts results above all else.{0:21:04.62}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.60,0:09:40.10,Main,Human,0,0,0,,And he’s harsh on everyone, \N himself included.{0:21:07.37}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.10,0:09:42.77,Main,Human,0,0,0,,That’s how he made it \N as a Gym Leader.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.65,0:09:44.73,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Harsh...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.11,0:09:51.28,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I’ll do my best! \N I’ll get Mr. Grusha{Honorifics note: Grusha-san} to approve of me!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.28,0:09:54.32,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,That’s right! \N You’ve gotta do all you can!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.16,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Show him what you’re made of!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.16,0:09:57.41,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.41,0:09:59.79,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote, let’s do our best together!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.04,0:10:05.58,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,Your implementation test \N is ready to begin.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.17,0:10:12.51,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Liko!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.51,0:10:14.22,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.77,0:10:20.56,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.98,0:10:31.82,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.82,0:10:33.99,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,So that’s where you were.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.36,0:10:36.49,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,I told you not to run ahead.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.25,0:10:50.50,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,It’s frigid out here.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.17,0:10:55.93,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Right, let’s get started.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.43,0:10:58.97,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Yes! Please, let’s!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.97,0:11:00.64,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Let’s go, Nyarote!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.93,0:11:06.65,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Let me show you a reality \N as icy-cold as snow.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.16,0:11:25.25,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.25,0:11:29.21,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,Hulkujira. Land Whale Pokémon. \N Ice type.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.21,0:11:33.26,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,It protects its body with powerful muscles \N and a thick layer of fat under its skin.{Partial Scarlet dex entry.}{ENgame seems fine}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.26,0:11:36.13,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,How’s she gonna deal with \N that difference in bulk?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.13,0:11:40.72,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Plus, Ice-type moves are super effective \N against Grass types. In other words...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.35,0:11:43.85,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I need to make sure \N its attacks don’t land.{Dread Hulkujira - game gender is male, but Liko doesn't really have a way of knowing.}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.52,0:11:48.60,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Well then, let the battle begin!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.60,0:11:50.94,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote! Lightning Speed!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.90,0:11:59.03,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,I get it! She’s moving around \N so her opponent can’t target her!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.03,0:12:00.41,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,That’s our Liko!{Sasuga. line}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.29,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,No good?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.29,0:12:10.29,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Hulkujira! Icicle Spears!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.21,0:12:15.05,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Dodge it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.47,0:12:19.55,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Then... Try{use} Magical Leaf!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.10,0:12:22.47,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Use Ice Spinner!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.02,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.06,0:12:34.28,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,But it was so slow before!{Dread Hulkujira}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.28,0:12:37.32,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,It’s a heck of a lot faster \N during that spinning attack!{Its spinning attack speed is [an order of magnitude higher/on another level]!}{Dread Hulkujira}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.32,0:12:39.11,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote, return!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.87,0:12:43.91,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Tebrim...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.33,0:12:45.20,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,{I'm }Counting on you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.75,0:12:50.17,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Trying to turn the tide, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.17,0:12:51.38,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Wasted effort.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.38,0:12:52.13,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Icicle Spears!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.75,0:12:57.13,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Tebrim, use Mind Power!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.98,0:13:11.69,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Okay, we can do this!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.99,0:13:24.70,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Tebrim, use a Brutal Swing attack!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.08,0:13:28.41,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,A head-on battle, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.79,0:13:30.08,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Aqua Break!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.84,0:13:37.80,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Tebrim, keep it up!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.80,0:13:39.17,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Ice Spinner!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.81,0:13:48.18,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Tebrim!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.90,0:13:57.65,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Thank you, Tebrim.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.11,0:13:59.90,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.03,0:14:06.78,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Now you have nothing left.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.62,0:14:12.54,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I’ve landed several attacks, \N but its defenses are solid...{Dread Hulkujira}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.08,0:14:16.17,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Ordinary attacks \N might not be enough...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.17,0:14:18.21,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Hulkujira! Ice Spinner!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.17,0:14:20.92,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.47,0:14:25.97,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Dodge it, Nyarote!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.26,0:14:30.47,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nearly there! \N Just hold on, Nyarote!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.14,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,It’s time I ended this.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.98,0:14:37.19,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Hulkujira! Icicle Spears!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.11,0:14:42.99,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Now! Fire a Magical Leaf \N into that big mouth!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.25,0:14:52.29,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.29,0:14:53.37,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.37,0:14:54.87,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Nice control!{sports term}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.87,0:14:55.62,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.04,0:15:00.63,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,It might have tough muscle all over its body, \N but it can’t buff up the inside of its mouth!{Dread Hulkujira x4 combo}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.55,0:15:06.30,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Hulkujira, return.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.30,0:15:10.10,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Guess you’ve got {\i1}something{\i0} to offer...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.60,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Then, next I’ll use...!
Comment: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:21.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part C}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.37,0:15:34.62,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,Tyltalis. Humming Pokémon. \N Dragon/Flying type.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.00,0:15:37.42,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,It sings in a beautiful soprano.{Partial Violet dex entry}{ENgame is correct}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.42,0:15:41.96,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,It has a kind disposition, but if it’s provoked, \N it will intimidate opponents with shrill cries...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.96,0:15:44.63,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,...before attacking them \N without mercy.{Shield dex entry}{swapped in intimidate for ikaku. left opponent as-is cause not sure what a good but more generic substitute would be--seems generally serviceable to me this way -ed}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.63,0:15:46.47,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Not good...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.47,0:15:50.68,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Grass-type attacks barely deal any damage \N to Dragon/Flying types.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.68,0:15:51.72,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,It’ll be fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.51,0:15:54.02,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Liko will think of something.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.73,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Tyltalis is a strong foe.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.73,0:16:01.52,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.27,0:16:05.86,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I fought against strong trainers \N in order to make it here.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.36,0:16:09.45,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,All that’s left is to do my best!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.53,0:16:13.74,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote, let’s go for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.87,0:16:16.25,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Lightning Speed!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.04,0:16:22.54,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,It didn’t connect!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.54,0:16:24.42,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Know your place.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.76,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Tyltalis, use Moonforce!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.34,0:16:31.76,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Magical Leaf!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.89,0:16:38.60,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,How long can you hold out?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.02,0:16:41.27,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Keep using Moonforce!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.15,0:16:45.53,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote, dodge it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.04,0:17:02.83,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,How can I hit a flying opponent?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.80,0:17:07.59,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,That’s it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.84,0:17:12.93,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.68,0:17:16.14,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Latch your bud onto Tyltalis!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.19,0:17:28.40,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Caught you!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.07,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote! Acrobatics!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.20,0:17:37.45,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.70,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Good work, Liko!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.16,0:17:40.96,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Now, Nyarote!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.96,0:17:43.92,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Shine... in full bloom!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.59,0:17:45.84,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Terastal!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.84,0:17:47.84,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Keep it going and bring it home!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.07,0:18:10.32,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Terastallizing now...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.61,0:18:14.70,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Battles are much like snowy mountains.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.70,0:18:20.54,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,They can turn on you in an instant.{ENgame: Battles are like mountains in winter—the situation can change in a heartbeat.}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.98,0:18:44.31,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Mr. Grusha{Honorifics note: Grusha-san} Terastallized too!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.31,0:18:48.19,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Wait, that could actually \N be {\i1}good{\i0} for Liko...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.19,0:18:49.11,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.11,0:18:54.36,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,It becoming an Ice Terastype means that \N Grass-type attacks should work now.{Dread Tyltalis - game gender is female but Dot has no way of knowing that}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.03,0:18:57.37,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,The type advantage has changed!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.62,0:19:00.33,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote, let’s go!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.33,0:19:01.95,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Magical Leaf!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.83,0:19:06.12,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Changing the type advantage \N won’t change the skill gap.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.92,0:19:08.67,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Ice Beam!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.40,0:19:30.77,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Despair is always close at hand.{ENgame: You’re always just one step away from devastation... The cold will leave you shaking.}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.15,0:19:34.69,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Shiver and fall into slumber.{Fall asleep while shivering.}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.67,0:19:49.21,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Oh no... Nyarote!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.89,0:20:09.44,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Tough luck, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.15,0:20:10.90,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.44,0:20:13.57,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Nyarote...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.57,0:20:14.86,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.57,0:20:17.49,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Don’t worry!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.49,0:20:20.70,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,You tried really hard \N and gave it all you’ve got.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.70,0:20:21.70,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm, mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.70,0:20:25.29,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,You lost the battle, \N but you could still pass.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.29,0:20:29.58,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,That’s right! He might look at \N how well you battled, instead of the results.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.58,0:20:31.63,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,That’s what happened with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.63,0:20:32.50,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.92,0:20:41.89,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Liko. Here are the results of \N your Terastal Course implementation test.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.31,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,You failed.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.35,0:20:49.39,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,No way... But she tried so hard!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.39,0:20:51.31,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Please let her try again!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.31,0:20:53.86,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,How hard she tried doesn’t matter.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.40,0:20:57.69,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,And there are no do-overs \N in real battles.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.69,0:21:00.24,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,No matter what, \N the results are all that matter.
Comment: 10,0:21:03.70,0:21:04.20,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.62,0:21:07.37,Main,Human,0,0,0,,He puts results above all else.{0:09:34.01}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.37,0:21:11.12,Main,Human,0,0,0,,{\t(3149,3649,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF)}And he’s harsh on everyone, \N himself included.{0:09:36.60}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.83,0:21:13.96,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,That’s simply how battles go.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.84,0:21:17.76,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Passing you, even though you lost?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.51,0:21:19.88,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,What a frigid joke.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.93,0:21:26.72,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.94,0:21:30.85,Main,Grusha,0,0,0,,Bye, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.07,0:21:36.23,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Liko...
Comment: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:45.53,Main,,0,0,0,,{Professor Friede's Pokémon Seminar A}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.24,0:21:47.24,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Friede here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.24,0:21:49.33,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,It’s time for my Pokémon Seminar!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.87,0:21:54.54,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Today, let’s take a look at \N the Land Whale Pokémon, Arukujira.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.54,0:21:57.92,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,A Pokémon that forms pods \N on snowy mountains.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.92,0:22:04.26,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,But do you know what Arukujira’s \N favorite food is—what it’s constantly eating?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.26,0:22:06.35,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,See the answer after the commercials!
Comment: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:07.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Comment: 0,0:23:37.52,0:23:37.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{Professor Friede's Pokémon Seminar B}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:38.31,0:23:40.52,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Now, time to announce \N the correct answer!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:41.57,0:23:44.11,Main,Friede,0,0,220,,The answer is C: Snow.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:44.78,0:23:48.95,Main,Friede,0,0,220,,Arukujira love the minerals found in snow.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:48.95,0:23:52.54,Main,Friede,0,0,220,,They spend their days \N walking and eating snow.
Comment: 0,0:24:00.54,0:24:00.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:01.17,0:24:03.59,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Well, the Terastal Course is over.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:04.09,0:24:06.51,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Hey, let’s stop by somewhere \N before we head back!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.51,0:24:08.18,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,No way! It’s too cold!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:08.18,0:24:11.10,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Don’t be like that! Let’s go!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:11.10,0:24:13.68,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Gah! Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.10,0:24:15.93,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,They{ all} sound happy...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:15.93,0:24:18.44,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Wait, huh? \N I got separated from them?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:18.44,0:24:20.36,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,What do I do? \N I’ve got a bad feeling...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.36,0:24:22.82,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Stuff like this always leads to \N some big event...{Times like this are when something tends to happen (story-wise)}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.82,0:24:26.24,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,And so! To be continued \N next time on Pocket Monsters!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:26.24,0:24:28.53,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Mt. Nappé and the Creeping Shadows
Dialogue: 10,0:24:28.53,0:24:29.78,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Don’t miss it!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,
