Dialogue: 11,0:01:27.65,0:01:31.03,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{=1047}{\blur0.6\fad(350,0)\1a&HFF&\t(305,350,\1a&H00&)}Together, we challenge, chasing the future
Dialogue: 11,0:01:31.03,0:01:32.03,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}(Let’s go!)
Dialogue: 11,0:01:32.03,0:01:34.70,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}We gather, let’s catch it, chasing tomorrow
Dialogue: 11,0:01:34.70,0:01:35.74,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}(Hey, let’s go!)
Dialogue: 11,0:01:35.74,0:01:39.16,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Never give up - Every time you fall, stand up
Dialogue: 11,0:01:39.16,0:01:41.29,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 11,0:01:41.29,0:01:42.79,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}(Take a step out, go!)
Dialogue: 11,0:01:42.79,0:01:43.58,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}(hey buddy)
Dialogue: 11,0:01:43.58,0:01:47.84,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Imagining, dreaming, with my friend (oh)
Dialogue: 11,0:01:47.84,0:01:50.63,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}The light ahead of us, so bright
Dialogue: 11,0:01:50.63,0:01:52.76,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Once it catches your eye
Dialogue: 11,0:01:52.76,0:01:54.93,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}The rest is easy, leave it to me
Dialogue: 11,0:01:54.93,0:01:58.77,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}You and I will add to our story (oh-oh)
Dialogue: 11,0:01:58.77,0:02:00.73,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Always a little bit more (We are)
Dialogue: 11,0:02:00.73,0:02:02.94,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Closer than yesterday (Best friends)
Dialogue: 11,0:02:02.94,0:02:07.07,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}I’m making my debut into a new world with you
Dialogue: 11,0:02:07.07,0:02:09.98,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}We’re the challengers
Dialogue: 11,0:02:09.98,0:02:14.49,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}It’s set into motion now, our fateful adventure
Dialogue: 11,0:02:14.49,0:02:18.08,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}We’re the challengers
Dialogue: 11,0:02:18.08,0:02:20.24,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Watch us, tell us...
Dialogue: 11,0:02:20.24,0:02:21.62,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}(hey buddy, let’s go)
Dialogue: 11,0:02:21.62,0:02:26.08,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}We are buddy-buddy-buddies, chasing piles of dreams
Dialogue: 11,0:02:26.08,0:02:28.17,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Wish it, and it’ll come true, you know it
Dialogue: 11,0:02:28.17,0:02:29.50,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Get over here, Challenger
Dialogue: 11,0:02:29.50,0:02:33.47,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Now, to chase spark-spark-sparkling bright tomorrows
Dialogue: 11,0:02:33.47,0:02:35.43,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Leap out into that vast sky
Dialogue: 11,0:02:35.43,0:02:38.22,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}You sparkling Challenger
Dialogue: 11,0:02:38.22,0:02:41.06,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}We’re the challengers
Dialogue: 11,0:02:41.06,0:02:45.94,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Hand in hand, flying up-up-up higher
Dialogue: 11,0:02:45.94,0:02:49.61,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}We’re the challengers
Dialogue: 11,0:02:49.61,0:02:51.36,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 11,0:02:51.36,0:02:52.90,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}(Take a step out, go!)
Dialogue: 11,0:02:52.90,0:02:55.70,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Let’s challenge
