Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.81,0:22:12.35,ED,,0,0,0,,{=1045}{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}Journey with buddy! Leap out!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.35,0:22:13.35,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}Turn up the heat!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.35,0:22:15.40,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}Ride on! In peak form! Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.40,0:22:16.90,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}Coolly say "Let me battle"
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.90,0:22:20.32,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}That mysterious power everyone has
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.32,0:22:23.41,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}I want it too, come look and listen with me
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.41,0:22:25.20,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}Heart pounding at the display (display)
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.20,0:22:26.83,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}Leap past it, runaway (Yeah)
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.83,0:22:31.37,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}Action! Dodging and weaving every which way
Dialogue: 10,0:22:31.37,0:22:34.92,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}The mystery in my pocket, it must be adventure
Dialogue: 10,0:22:34.92,0:22:38.67,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}Soaking up sun and rain, that's how seeds sprout
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.67,0:22:40.59,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}Gotta beat my yesterday 1,2,3,4!!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.59,0:22:43.30,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}Even by the smallest margin (Trial & error)
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.30,0:22:45.59,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}It's a new personal best!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:45.59,0:22:47.30,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&\c&H2725F5&}Tel{\c&HFFFFFF&}ling a {\c&H2725F5&}r{\c&HFFFFFF&}e{\c&H2725F5&}a{\c&HFFFFFF&}l hero-to-{\c&H2725F5&}c{\c&HFFFFFF&}ome's {\c&H2725F5&}S{\c&HFFFFFF&}tory{lit. Story of [one who] can become a hero}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:47.30,0:22:49.18,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}Look to the fu{\c&HFE21A3&}t{\c&HFFFFFF&}ure, som{\c&HFE21A3&}e{\c&HFFFFFF&}day I'{\c&HFE21A3&}l{\c&HFFFFFF&}l get t{\c&HFE21A3&}o {\c&HFFFFFF&}cla{\c&HFE21A3&}i{\c&HFFFFFF&}m {\c&HFE21A3&}V{\c&HFFFFFF&}ictory{lit. If you look to tomorrow, sooner or later [I] claim Victory}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:49.18,0:22:50.77,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}Nice to meet you, to the beat y'all
Dialogue: 10,0:22:50.77,0:22:53.06,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}It's super promising!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:53.06,0:22:56.73,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}I'm all set to hone my skills until I'm satisfied
Dialogue: 10,0:22:56.73,0:22:58.86,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}(Ready, hop! Ready, jump!)
Dialogue: 10,0:22:58.86,0:23:01.19,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}And go! Head past the furthest reaches
Dialogue: 10,0:23:01.19,0:23:03.49,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}Never bind myself with limits
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.49,0:23:06.78,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}Just seek out my way, 'til I catch it for sure
Dialogue: 10,0:23:06.78,0:23:08.70,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}(Beyond!) Hope's at a perfect 100%
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.70,0:23:10.45,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}(Reload!) Keep trying, every time
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.45,0:23:12.16,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}Again, again, again...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.16,0:23:14.25,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}Hello, future!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:14.25,0:23:16.67,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}Journey with buddy! Leap out!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:16.67,0:23:17.67,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}Turn up the heat!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.67,0:23:19.46,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}Ride on! In peak form! Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:19.46,0:23:21.42,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}Coolly say "Let me battle"
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.55,0:23:30.97,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}Aee aye (Hey! Hey! Hey! Hey!...)
Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.97,0:23:32.02,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}Alright, stay tuned, come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:32.02,0:23:36.19,ED,,0,0,0,,{=1046}{\fad(0,520)\blur0.6\4a&HA0&}See you again tomorrow!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,
